## Constraints
- Smallest correct change. No unrequested scope.
- Stay inside Allowed Files. Return BLOCKED before broadening.
- No assertion weakening. No test deletion or skip without explicit packet authorization.
- GREEN-SUITE and REFACTOR packets must not smuggle in behavior changes.
- No new file > 400 lines. No existing source file pushed > 500 lines.
- Worker runs locally only. Do not push to remote until Final Verify is green.

