```bash
[VERIFY_COMMAND]
```

## Apply Checklist Required
- [ ] Worker must complete `docs/APPLY_CHECKLIST.md` before returning DONE.
- [ ] Result packet must explicitly confirm checklist status.

## Required Return
- Fill `docs/WORKER_RESULT_PACKET.md`.
- Include PASS/FAIL per criterion, iteration count, diff stats, commands with exit codes, Path ID evidence, blockers.
- Body target <= 200 lines.
- Full diff requested? NO

## Escalate If (Return BLOCKED)
- Scope must expand beyond Allowed Files.
- Business/product rule is unclear.
- Security or privacy concern appears.
- Acceptance criterion appears wrong or unreachable.
- Allowed Commands are insufficient.
- Iteration count would exceed Max iterations.
- Refactor needed before safe completion.